{"tid":2157714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為了不想被對方拒絕 便先自行拒絕了全世界","createTime":"2020-08-15T08:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T08:37:40.000Z","uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96b932d755ce86f083a5b54ea94645de3ecff11d","tid":2157714,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"即使無可避免與人接觸 仍保持刺蝟般的距離<br />\n不要站得太近 也不要離我太遠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3103b58272457e7f8d1284d377e39e6caea845b9","tid":2157714,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"「我是孤星入命的人，父母早死，只好跟哥哥相依為命。可能因為我是孤兒，從小我就懂得保護自己。我知道要想不被人拒絕，最好的方法就是先拒絕別人。因為這個原因，我再也沒有回去。其實那邊也不錯，可惜我已經不能回頭了。我的命書裡說過：夫妻宮太陽化忌，婚姻有實無名，想不到是真的。」"},{"pid":"887f200e30d33c84b6bf84ae6f896000af3191e0","tid":2157714,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"每個人都渴望有獨立的自由但還是想接觸對方與之交流"},{"pid":"39730870fdb758cfcb7a6ce80144ef3342332100","tid":2157714,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FctGQCB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFctGQCB.png&h=202f17d2&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"}]}